          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 7 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program. The script targets the tension that arrives with bills: the dread of opening them, the resentment of money going out, the belief that bills and struggle are the same thing. Use it before a regular bill-payment session.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
